                <p>EHE was founded in 1913 as the first medical center devoted to healthy individuals, with the mission to equip patients with lifestyle management tools to live their healthiest lives. Our pioneering approach immediately won acclaim and for decades, EHE has had the privilege of serving some of America's biggest companies, making them healthier and higher performing.</p>
          </div>
          <div class='small-12 large-6 column'>
              <p>EHE's experience is matched only by our continuing innovation. We are committed to providing the very best in prevention and wellness, made possible by advancing technology and a uniquely personalized approach to each and every patient.</p>
              <p>After more than a century of excellence, our story is only starting.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
